    <item>
      <title>市场动荡之际投资者需关注鲍威尔的语气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/investors-to-watch-powell-s-tone-as-market-teeters-taking-stock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着美联储为期两天的会议开始，投资者已经接受了美联储这次可能不会降息的事实。但由于股市处于脆弱时期，他们正在寻找美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔发出的有关通胀走向的信号。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/investors-to-watch-powell-s-tone-as-market-teeters-taking-stock</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 10:30:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
