      <title>南非民主联盟表示致力于组建团结政府</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/south-africa-s-da-party-says-it-s-committed-to-unity-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二大政党表示，该党仍致力于组建该国所谓的民族团结政府，并努力解决总统拉马福萨批准的新法律引发的争议。兰特上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/south-africa-s-da-party-says-it-s-committed-to-unity-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:56:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧元区银行收紧企业信贷标准 创 2023 年以来最大降幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/euro-zone-banks-tighten-firms-credit-standards-most-since-2023</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行表示，欧元区银行已将企业信贷标准收紧至 2023 年以来最大幅度，这打破了企业贷款快速复苏以支持投资的希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/euro-zone-banks-tighten-firms-credit-standards-most-since-2023</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 09:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
